			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">In this study, our objective is to understand and analyze the environmental impacts caused by lithium production from brine in Clayton Valley, Nevada, using a new method to produce lithium carbonate without using large evaporation ponds. Direct Lithium Extraction technologies strive to address the environmental and technoeconomic limitations of traditional evaporitic methods. The objective is to eliminate the need for open-air evaporation ponds. Numerous alternative technologies have been proposed, such as ion exchange resins, thermally assisted processes, and electrochemical methods . </common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">研究的目标是了解和分析在内华达州克莱顿谷利用卤水生产锂对环境造成的影响，这种生产碳酸锂的新方法无需使用大型蒸发池。直接锂提取技术致力于解决传统蒸发法在环境和技术经济方面的局限性。其目标是消除对露天蒸发池的需求。已经提出了许多替代技术，如离子交换树脂、热辅助工艺和电化学方法。</common:generalComment>
		</dataSetInformation>
